        "Params": "{1: '2', 2: '0.25'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 13,
        "ActionId": 12,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: '...Our investigation shows Cyril was the leader of the Punishing Rebels. Not sure if he was the only leader, or if there were others.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 14,
        "ActionId": 13,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'But we are certain that he had everything planned from the moment he approached the operation.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 15,
        "ActionId": 14,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'They aren\\'t a significant threat to Babylonia yet. But considering how little time they had to prepare, and how quickly they assembled with limited resources...', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 16,
        "ActionId": 15,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'And their ability to plan and execute such an ambush...', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 17,
        "ActionId": 16,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'All I can say is, thanks to you, we didn\\'t lose Halcyon 2.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 18,
        "ActionId": 17,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'That group mostly consists of ex-soldiers of the old government who aren\\'t satisfied with the operation commands we have now. They have already left since Cyril exposed himself.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 19,
        "ActionId": 18,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'We managed to kill or capture some of them, but a lot had escaped and are still active.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 20,
        "ActionId": 19,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Hassen', 3: 'If we do nothing, they may grow into a large threat.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 21,
        "ActionId": 20,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 201,
        "IsBlock": null,
